カメラが遠近感をシミュレートするかを設定する
When ortho is ''true'', camera's viewing volume is defined by ::ref::orthographicSize.\\
When orthographic is ''false'', camera's viewing volume is defined by ::ref::fieldOfView.

SA: [[wiki:class-Camera|camera component]], ::ref::transparencySortMode.
CONVERTEXAMPLE
BEGIN EX
	// Set the camera to be orthograpghic

	camera.orthographic = true;
END EX
